data.name: ButtonAdd.ToolTip
data.value: add to the list the profile written in the combobox

data.name: ButtonDel.ToolTip
data.value: delete from the list the profile selected in the combobox

data.name: ButtonStop.ToolTip
data.value: -n, --dry-run : start the synchronization without doing modifications

data.name: CbRedir.ToolTip
data.value: redirect the standard and error streams to the licielrsync text box (you may need to disable this to access the password prompt with authenticated transfers)

data.name: CbHideWindows.ToolTip
data.value: hide the command prompt (you may need to disable this to access the password prompt with authenticated transfers)

data.name: ButtonPause.ToolTip
data.value: -n, --dry-run : start the synchronization without doing modifications

data.name: ButtonTest.ToolTip
data.value: -n, --dry-run : start the synchronization without doing modifications

data.name: CbShowCmd.ToolTip
data.value: show the command line on the status bar

data.name: CbReadable.ToolTip
data.value: -h, --human-readable : output numbers in a human-readable format

data.name: CbChecksum.ToolTip
data.value: -c, --checksum : skip based on checksum, not mod-time & size

data.name: CbDelta.ToolTip
data.value: --no-whole-file : force to don't send whole files (with delta-xfer algorithm)

data.name: CbExistingOnly.ToolTip
data.value: --existing : skip creating new files on receiver

data.name: CbSizeOnly.ToolTip
data.value: --size-only : skip files that match in size

data.name: CbNewer.ToolTip
data.value: -u, --update : skip files that are newer on the receiver

data.name: CbIgnoreTimes.ToolTip
data.value: --ignore-times : don't skip files that match in size and mod-time

data.name: CbExisting.ToolTip
data.value: --ignore-existing : skip updating files that already exist on receiver

data.name: CbDelete.ToolTip
data.value: --delete : delete extraneous files from destination dirs

data.name: CbWinCompat.ToolTip
data.value: --modify-window=2 : known to fixe problems on some old windows (FAT)

data.name: CbPermWin.ToolTip
data.value: --backup-nt-streams --restore-nt-streams : preserve acl security in windows (requires a patched version of rsync -ntstreams)

data.name: $this.Text
data.value: LicielRsync - A multi-threaded interface for Rsync on Windows - rsync.samba.org
